* Iron Raptor dropped down to her other knee and snarled as she felt a 
little energy drain from Rampage and into her. She hatted the feel of it but 
she needed it badly!
Mech fluid gushed from between Rampage's claws and she roared as she felt 
gears begin to snap in her leg.*

" I could care less if your spark could replace the universe, you SHALL NOT 
WIN!!!!!!!!!"

* With as much energy as she could muster she kicked her leg up( the one 
Rampage is attached to) and slammed her body into it and against the far 
wall, there was a chance that she would break her own leg but if it crushed 
the crab attached to it she didn't care!!!
The base wall buckled and broke open as she slammed into it, now she lay out 
in the open outdoors, her leg broken and bleeding.
Iron Raptor snarled in pain, weather her act had gotten Rampage she didn't 
know*
